snippet.title: Hamefura - Fortune Lover Game - Geordo Route (Fan Translation)
snippet.description:
This is a fan translation of Geordo's route in the Fortune Lover game which was given with the Japanese blu-rays of the season 1 of the My Next Life As A Villainess: All Routes Lead To Doom / Hamefura anime.

*Game:* Fortune Lover (Trial version)

*Series:*: My Next Life as a Villainess: All Routes Lead to Doom!

*Game Platform:* PC

*How to get it?:* Buy Volume 1 of the Japanese blurays of the My Next Life As A Villainess: All Routes Lead To Doom anime (season 1).

*Route:* Geordo Route
